INFORMATION

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

CHANGES

* Version 3.9.0 (2020-12-31)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE

* Version 3.8.1 (2020-11-29)
B: Adjust return code for monit service check

* Version 3.8.0 (2020-11-29)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (nginx_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 3.7.2 (2020-11-19)
E: Ensure lineinfile tasks can create file if missing

* Version 3.7.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 3.7.0 (2020-10-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.8
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.7

* Version 3.6.0 (2020-05-19)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.7
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.6

* Version 3.5.0 (2020-04-30)
F: Add option to define log_format main (nginx_log_format_main)
F: Add option to define log_format main_ssl (nginx_log_format_main_ssl)

* Version 3.4.1 (2020-04-18)
E: Enable TLS version 1.3 by default

* Version 3.4.0 (2019-11-08)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE

* Version 3.3.0 (2019-10-18)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.6
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.5

* Version 3.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 3.1.0 (2019-04-27)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.5
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.4

* Version 3.0.3 (2019-02-08)
E: Add possibility to disable 'ssl_dhparam' and 'ssl_ecdh_curve' parameters

* Version 3.0.2 (2019-02-06)
B: Correct default value of 'nginx_config' parameter (array instead of string)

* Version 3.0.1 (2019-02-05)
E: Use Jinja2 argument 'indentfirst' instead of 'first' (support older Jinja2 versions)

* Version 3.0.0 (2019-02-05)
C: Redesign 'nginx_config' option (alter config variable to string)

* Version 2.1.0 (2019-01-13)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE

* Version 2.0.0 (2018-12-17)
C: Rename config parameters
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 1.4.0 (2018-10-20)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.4
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.3

* Version 1.3.0 (2018-09-05)
F: Add options to disable 'ssl_dhparam' and 'ssl_ecdh_curve'

* Version 1.2.0 (2018-07-01)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE

* Version 1.1.3 (2018-06-12)
E: Correct 'command' variable names

* Version 1.1.2 (2018-06-01)
E: Remove needless notify from 'command generate dhparam' task

* Version 1.1.1 (2018-05-31)
E: Correct 'command' variable names

* Version 1.1.0 (2018-05-22)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 1.0.4 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 1.0.3 (2018-04-16)
E: Remove needless else statement in Jinja2 template

* Version 1.0.2 (2018-04-15)
B: Correct package and service variable names
E: Improve Jinja2 templating

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-04-14)
E: Remove duplicate variables

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-04-14)
E: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 0.11.2 (2018-04-06)
E: Change default 'ssl_protocols' value from 'TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2' to 'TLSv1.2'
E: Change default 'ssl_ciphers' value from 'AES256+EECDH:AES256+EDH' to 'AES256+EECDH'

* Version 0.11.1 (2018-04-05)
E: Change curve for ECDHE ciphers from 'secp384r1' to 'secp521r1'

* Version 0.11.0 (2018-04-04)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.3
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.2

* Version 0.10.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.9.3 (2018-02-20)
E: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 0.9.2 (2017-12-26)
E: Move 'command generate dhparam' task

* Version 0.9.1 (2017-12-08)
E: Ensure role works in check mode
E: Avoid usage of raw module
E: Improve regular expression of grep command

* Version 0.9.0 (2017-10-18)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.2
C: Drop support for OpenBSD 6.1

* Version 0.8.0 (2017-08-26)
