* Version 0.7.0 (2017-06-19)
F: Add option to specify a curve for ECDHE ciphers (ssl_ecdh_curve)

* Version 0.6.0 (2017-05-05)
F: Add DH parameters for DHE ciphers

* Version 0.5.0 (2017-04-16)
C: Add support for OpenBSD 6.1
